results.title: Fix MCP parameter rendering for arrays and objects in Claude logs
results.author: Copilot
results.impact_rationale: Fixes bug causing '[object Object]' rendering in Claude log summaries for MCP tools with structured parameters. Affects tools like serena::ToolsSearch. Medium impact as it improves debugging experience.
results.urgency_rationale: Recent PR (< 1 hour old). Improves log readability for debugging. Moderate urgency - helpful but not blocking.
results.quality_rationale: Good description with before/after examples. Comprehensive test coverage (9 new tests). Draft status, CI pending. Well-documented fix.
results.action_explanation: Bug fix with good test coverage. Draft status suggests needs review before merge. Fast-track once CI passes.

results.title: Fix firewall SSL-bump field extraction in frontmatter parser
results.author: Copilot
results.impact_rationale: Fixes critical configuration fields (ssl-bump, allow-urls) not being extracted from YAML, blocking users from using documented firewall HTTPS inspection features. High impact.
results.urgency_rationale: Fixes issue #13908. Blocks documented feature usage. Age: 4.8 hours. High priority issue from Schema Consistency Analysis discussion.
results.quality_rationale: Excellent description with code examples. 8 unit tests + integration test. Not draft but CI pending. Fixes known issue.
results.action_explanation: Critical bug fix for documented feature. Well-tested, fixes known issue. Fast-track once CI passes despite medium risk (security-related changes).

results.title: Fix Serena container selection array handling bug
results.author: Copilot
results.impact_rationale: Fixes array parsing bug affecting 15 workflows using Serena with array syntax. Workflows with 'serena: ["go"]' failed due to container selection not handling array format. High impact.
results.urgency_rationale: Fixes issue #13857 affecting 15 workflows. Age: 12.5 hours. Already triaged once with labels. Moderate urgency - workflow failures.
results.quality_rationale: Good description with background explanation. 4 new test cases covering array formats and edge cases. Draft status, CI pending, 4 comments with discussion.
results.action_explanation: Critical bug fix affecting multiple workflows. Already triaged. Well-tested but draft status suggests needs final review. Fast-track once CI passes and ready for merge.
